&lt;p&gt;This is a fantastic opportunity to join our Strategy Team on a 12 month fixed term contract, supporting the hospital and our colleagues to provide brilliant care for our patients, now and in the future.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for an individual with excellent clerical skills, who can provide comprehensive administrative, clerical, and committee support to our team; Working closely with teams across the Trust as well as externally.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a varied and interesting role, requiring someone who is well organised, able to work using their own initiative, and is a good communicator.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a full time post working 37.5 hours per week, however part time hours may be considered&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Joe Turner, Business Planning Manager/Analyst, Joe.Turner2@nhs.net or 07769875918&lt;/p&gt;
